## Why This Question Is Asked

This question evaluates the ability to design privacy-preserving retention controls at the device edge, balancing storage, CPU, and regulatory costs while quantifying the business impact of data minimization.

## Key Concepts

- On-device policy engines and interpreters
- Data minimization and retention windows
- Batch policy delivery and anonymized audit deltas
- Compliance costs and telemetry design

## Code Example

```javascript
// Policy evaluator
function shouldDelete(event, policy) {
  const rule = policy.findRule(event.type);
  return event.timestamp < Date.now() - policy.getRetentionPeriod(rule);
}
```

## Why This Is Asked

